      <title>欧洲央行官员就降息幅度如何才能提振经济展开激烈争论</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/ecb-officials-to-lock-horns-over-how-much-cuts-can-boost-economy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行官员一致认为，降低利率是提振该地区不稳定经济的必要措施。不过，降息究竟能起到多大作用，仍存在很大争议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/ecb-officials-to-lock-horns-over-how-much-cuts-can-boost-economy</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
